title: The SML and Chilly baby's gender reveal *EMOTIONAL*
author: Chilly
description:
So happy to share probably the most important and special moment of our entire lives.. I hope you guys enjoyed being able to watch. I look forward to looking back on this video a few years from now.
WARNING, this video WILL have you crying.

We also shared some personal information with you guys and why this baby is so much more meaningful to us.
This baby literally saved both of our lives and it was something we didn't know we needed.
